Warhead: All right! Rage, Inferno, join the rest of the patrol. 
Nightshade, Drillbit, tighten the ranks. I want both of you at ten 
meters of distance from me.

Energon build-up started to form on him. He stopped a few seconds from 
the slight pain, but regained composure.

Warhead: Energon is strong on this mudball... Everybody back to beast 
mode!

He took a step back and transformed to his gunship mode.
